    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've really got to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape\u2014not a single scratch or mark on it! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I\u2019m only selling it because I\u2019m downsizing, but I know whoever gets the keys is going to be so happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat! \u2728",
