    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the 'mint' standard. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed, presenting in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are flawless, showing no signs of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain supple and matte, with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing. All interior surfaces, from the dashboard to the door cards, are pristine, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, 'open-checkbook' service history. The engine bay is immaculate, and the drive is tight, quiet, and powerful. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks and performs as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
